  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><include href=\"../Passage/VR596596.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">The student claims that the reaction is an oxidation-reduction reaction. Which of the following statements correctly describes a change in oxidation number as the decomposition reaction proceeds?</p>\n",
